reviewText: A great comedy performance by Brett Butler, perhaps best know for her long-running TV series "Grace Under Fire". Great wit, polished performance. If you like funny stuff, you'll like this. A "must see" special performance! Get it! Se'll have a new disc out later this year.
This show is nowhere near as good as her first one, "The child ain't right."  I laughed a couple of times in this one but overall I didn't like it much.
